@startuml
title Séquence métier — Traiter un signalement (Report)
' ------------------------------------------------------------------
' Style impression A4 (PFE FSEG) — lisibilité : polices ~11–12 pt visibles,
' DPI 240, retour à la ligne des messages. Inclure juste après la ligne title.
' Export PNG pour Word/LaTeX : viser largeur <= zone utile A4 (~17 cm).
' ------------------------------------------------------------------
scale max 1550 width
skinparam dpi 240
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam handwritten false
skinparam HyperlinkUnderline false

skinparam defaultFontSize 12
skinparam titleFontSize 16
skinparam ArrowFontSize 11
skinparam arrowThickness 1.25
skinparam wrapWidth 220
skinparam NoteFontSize 10
skinparam LegendFontSize 10
skinparam footerFontSize 10
skinparam headerFontSize 10

skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam ParticipantPadding 14
skinparam BoxPadding 8
skinparam LifeLineBorderColor #444444
skinparam LifeLineBackgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam ArrowColor #222222
skinparam ActorBorderColor #222222
skinparam ActorBackgroundColor #EEF6FF
skinparam ParticipantBorderColor #333333
skinparam ParticipantBackgroundColor #FFFFFF

skinparam DatabaseBackgroundColor #F8F8F8
skinparam EntityBackgroundColor #F8FFF8
skinparam ControlBackgroundColor #FFF8F0
skinparam BoundaryBackgroundColor #F5F5FF
actor Admin as admin
boundary "Administration" as UI
control "Contrôleur" as Svc
entity "Base de données" as DB
queue "BullMQ : send-email" as Queue

admin -> UI: Choisir un signalement, définir la résolution
UI -> Svc: POST /api/admin/reports/:id/resolve { resolution, actionOnProject?, actionOnComment? }

Svc -> DB: Trouver le signalement par id
DB --> Svc: report

alt report.status == "PENDING"
  Svc -> DB: Mettre à jour report.status = "RESOLVED"/"DISMISSED",\nresolvedBy = admin.id, resolvedAt = now(), resolution
  ' ===== MEDIUM: Optional project action =====
  alt actionOnProject == "DEACTIVATE"
    Svc -> DB: transitionProjectStatus(project, SUSPENDED)\n+ rejectionReason = "Suspendu suite à un signalement (modération)"\n+ rejectedBy = admin.id ; rejectedAt = now()
    Svc -> DB: Notification (créateur) type PROJECT_SUSPENDED (avec motif)
  else actionOnProject == "WARNING"
    Svc -> DB: Notification (créateur) type PROJECT_WARNING (avec motif)
  end
  ' ===== MEDIUM: Optional comment action =====
  alt report.commentId != null and actionOnComment == "HIDE_COMMENT"
    Svc -> DB: Mettre à jour comment.isHidden = true,\nhiddenReason = "...", hiddenBy = admin.id, hiddenAt = now()
  else report.commentId != null and actionOnComment == "DELETE_COMMENT"
    Svc -> DB: Mettre à jour comment.isHidden = true + marquer deletedAt,\ndeletedBy = admin.id, deletedByRole = "ADMIN"
  end
  Svc -> DB: Notification (reporter) type REPORT_RESOLVED, relatedEntityId = report.id
  Svc -> DB: AuditLog (action=\"RESOLVE_REPORT\", details:{ status, actionOnProject, actionOnComment, hasCommentTarget })
  Svc -> Queue: enqueueEmailForNotifications(notifications)\n(sans bloquer ; selon la politique e-mails)
  Svc --> UI: 200
  UI --> admin: Signalement traité
else
  Svc --> UI: 400 Signalement déjà traité
end

note right of Svc
  **Action sur le projet :**
  - `DEACTIVATE` → projet SUSPENDED + notification `PROJECT_SUSPENDED`.
  - `WARNING` → notification `PROJECT_WARNING` (sans changement de statut).
  **Action sur un commentaire (si report.commentId existe) :**
  - `HIDE_COMMENT` → commentaire masqué (retiré du public).
  - `DELETE_COMMENT` → commentaire supprimé (suppression logique) + masqué.
  **Notifications :** création in-app dans la transaction ; e-mail en file (BullMQ) après commit.
end note

@enduml
